# readPacketObjects(completionHandler:)

**Instance Method**

Read multiple IP packets from the TUN interface.

## Declaration

```swift
func readPacketObjects(completionHandler: @escaping ([NEPacket]) -> Void)
```

```swift
func readPacketObjects() async -> [NEPacket]
```

## Handling IP packets

- **writePacketObjects(_:)**: Write multiple IP packets to the TUN interface.
- **readPackets(completionHandler:)**: Reads IP packets from the TUN interface.
- **writePackets(_:withProtocols:)**: Writes IP packets to the TUN interface.
